" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hoshikawa_sara_became_the_72nd_vtuber_in_history_to_reach_1_million_youtube_subscribers.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hoshikawa_sara_became_the_72nd_vtuber_in_history_to_reach_1_million_youtube_subscribers.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/hoshikawa_sara_became_the_72nd_vtuber_in_history_to_reach_1_million_youtube_subscribers.png?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="Sara Hoshikawa 订阅人数突破 100 万，VTuber 历史第 72 位" class="wp-image-110362" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube</figcaption></figure><p>这是历史上所有VTuber中实现这一目标的第72人，也是同一人才所属VTuber团体Nijisanji中的第5人（整个Nijisanji项目中的第7人（包括毕业生））。自2019年10月19日首次分配以来，这一目标已在1533天内实现。</p><p>星川莎拉于 2019 年 10 月 17 日从 VTuber 团体 Nijisanji 中首次亮相。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【100万人耐力】唱到100万人订阅！我想欢迎大家！ [Sara Hoshikawa/Nijisanji] #Sara Hoshikawa 100万人" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-4KTpl5nz4s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="kwibz65919165095f4" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
